messages.message:
FYI, we are adding some versioning to our docs repo, starting from 22.04.0 we will have a release branch with the same name (`release-22.04.0`) in instabase-docs git repo and our DOCS_TAG in instabase repo will be set to that branch (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/commit/c7fa7e4cbbf15b5b25e1b8a485d2626ec5404613)

how would this affect you?
for every cherry-picking in the instabase repo that involves with doc update, you would have to cherry-pick the doc change to the corresponding docs release branch as well, ib-cp-bot is installed in the docs repo as well and hopefully that will make things easier for you

feel free to let us know if you have any questions or concerns
